{
  "stem": "16345.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rumors around camps were when the Germans wanted to show off some of their camps to the Red Cross, they took them to one of their show camps, like Theresienstadt was one of the what we called a country club camp, where the Germans kept up just for the sake of being able to show it.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly, we were dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For instance, the, the most vivid one of these things was the last camp, my last camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It sounds ominous-- the last camp-- Ludwigslust.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In northern Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's spelled L-U-D-W-I-G-L-U-S-T.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was probably the-- my worst camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not that the others were that much better, but my memories of it are worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, it was sand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was always cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a sort of dirty brown sand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were billeted in buildings that had no floors, had no roofs, and had no windows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when, when it rained, which was quite often, we were, we were staying in mud most of the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In this camp, we were left alone more than in most other camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, they didn't supervise us by-- minute by minute or hour by hour.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we could, the prisoners would build little fires and roast whatever they could catch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think when we came to this camp, there was a large population of rats and cats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Within several weeks, the rats and cats both were being roasted on those little fires.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in, in, in this camp, my buddy and I organized a jar of oysters that had been thrown into the garbage from the guards' mess, guards' cafeteria.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we thought we, we'd, we'd really run into some good luck.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
